# Expense Operating Policy Acquisition Total Amount

## identifier
de13046

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, during the relevant period, of all fixed and variable costs as recognised under Australian Accounting Standards incurred when acquiring new business including those related to commissions and other incremental expenses.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Expense.Operating.PolicyAcquisitionTotal.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr2.02.13
- period=duration
